urn /ɜːn/

1. N-COUNT An urn is a container in which a dead person's ashes are kept. 骨灰瓮 

例： ...a funeral urn. …一个骨灰瓮。 

2. N-COUNT An urn is a metal container used for making a large quantity of tea or coffee and keeping it hot. (用于泡茶或咖啡并保温的金属) 大壶 

例： ...the ten gallon coffee urn. …那只10加仑的咖啡壶。

